imes of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons}}\n*{{Bollywood Hungama|6163891}}\n*{{IMDb name}}\n*[http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/calendar-girls-a-very-emotional-film-akanksha-puri/ Indian Express]\n*[http://www.ibtimes.co.in/interview-salman-khan-reason-i-am-into-industry-says-calendar-girls-actress-akanksha-puri-647889 IBTimes]\n*[http://www.mid-day.com/articles/calendar-girls-has-a-character-inspired-by-shilpa-shettys-life/16547193 Mid-day]\n*[http://www.rediff.com/movies/interview/it-was-difficult-to-shoot-in-a-bikini/20150727.htm Rediff]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Puri, Akanksha}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Indian film actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Hindi cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Tamil cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Malayalam cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Kannada cinema]]\n[[Category:21st-century Indian actresses]]\n[[Category:Female models from Madhya Pradesh]]\n[[Category:Actresses from Bhopal]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Indian model, and film actress}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=December 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Akanksha Puri\n| image              = Akanksha Puri attending the LFW 2016 on Day 3.jpg\n| caption            = Puri at the LFW 2016\n| native_name        = \n| native_name_lang   = \n| birth_name         = \n| birth_date         = {{birth date and age|1984|8|26|df=yes}}\n| birth_place        = [[Bhopal]], [[Madhya Pradesh]], India\n| death_date         = \n| death_place        = \n| nationality        = Indian\n| occupation         = Actress, model\n| years_active       = 2013\u2013present\n}}\n\n'''Akanksha Puri''' (born 26 August 1984) is Indian model, and film actress, known for her work in [[Malayalam]] , [[Tamil cinema|Tamil]], and [[Bollywood]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5462740/|title=Akanksha Puri IMdb |publisher=imdb.com |accessdate=31 August 2015}}</ref> She made her [[bollywood]] debut with [[Madhur Bhandarkar]]'s 2015 drama film ''[[Calendar Girls (2015 film)|Calendar Girls]]''<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/-akanksha-puri-after-calendar-girls-i-was-only-offered-erotic-roles/articleshow/59220181.cms|title=Akanksha Puri: After 'Calendar Girls', I was only offered erotic roles - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.in/interview-salman-khan-reason-i-am-into-industry-says-calendar-girls-actress-akanksha-puri-647889|title=Interview: 'Salman Khan is the reason I am into the industry', says 'Calendar Girls' actress Akanksha Puri|last=IBTimes|work=International Business Times, India Edition|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/malayalam/movies/news/Akanksha-Puri-is-Prithvirajs-heroine/articleshow/47685814.cms|title=Akanksha Puri is Prithviraj's heroine - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref> and is currently playing lead role of [[Adi Parashakti|Mata AdiParashakti]] and her avatars in the show [[Vighnaharta Ganesha]] from 22 August 2017.\n\nAkanksha took up modelling projects during her short stint as an international cabin crew. She was then spotted by big production house in south following which she bagged her first project as an actor in a Tamil movie.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://m.timesofindia.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Madhur-Bhandarkars-Calendar-girl-Akanksha-was-Vijay-Mallyas-handpicked-Kingfisher-cabin-crew/articleshow/48956376.cms|title=Madhur Bhandarkar's Calendar girl Akanksha was Vijay Mallya's handpicked Kingfisher cabin crew - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Calendar-Girl-Akanksha-Puri-roots-for-dry-Holi/articleshow/51511812.cms|title=Calendar Girl Akanksha Puri roots for dry Holi - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Vinayagar Serial Parvathi Glamorous Hot photo !|url=http://www.pakka.tv/entertainment/cine-news/vinayagar-serial-parvathi-glamorous-hot-photo---------9053/|work=PakkaTv|date=5 June 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Early life and background==\nAkanksha Puri hails from [[Madhya Pradesh]] and has done her schooling from a convent school in [[Bhopal]]\n=Personal Life=\nAkanksha was dating [[Paras Chhabra|Paras Chabra]] (fame from [[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 13)|Bigg Boss 13]]) from 2017 to 2019 however he said in the show he is not interested in her and want to end the relationship because of her possessive nature. Hearing this, She gave interviews to the media stating she pays for his clothes, shoes, rent and even pays his mother while he is away. Paras denied this and they have now broken up post his stint with [[Bigg Boss (Hindi season 13)|Bigg Boss 13]]\n\n<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/akanksha-puri-trains-rigorously-for-her-upcoming-show-vignahartha-ganesha/articleshow/59860562.cms|title=Akanksha Puri trains rigorously for her upcoming show Vignahartha Ganesha - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.easterneye.eu/akanksha-puri-wont-take-projects-long-part-vighnaharta-ganesh/|title=AKANKSHA PURI WON'T TAKE UP ANY OTHER PROJECTS AS LONG AS SHE IS A PART OF \"VIGHNAHARTA GANESH\"! - Eastern Eye|date=2017-08-12|work=Eastern Eye|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171212194836/https://www.easterneye.eu/akanksha-puri-wont-take-projects-long-part-vighnaharta-ganesh/|archive-date=12 December 2017|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodhungama.com/videos/celeb-interviews/i-feel-i-have-the-perfect-curves-akanksha-puri/|title=Watch \"I Feel I Have The Perfect CURVES\": Akanksha Puri Now - Bollywood Hungama|last=Hungama|first=Bollywood|work=Bollywood Hungama|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Film\n!Role\n!Language \t\n|-\n| 2013 ||'' [[Alex Pandian]]'' ||  || [[Tamil language|Tamil]]\t\n|-\n| 2014 || ''Tihar'' || Mukundan|| Tamil\n|-\n| 2014 || ''[[Praise the Lord (film)|Praise the Lord]] '' || Annie || Malayalam\t\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Lodde]] '' || || [[Kannada]]\t\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Samrajyam II: Son of Alexander]] '' ||Saira || Malayalam\t\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Calendar Girls (2015 film)|Calendar Girls]] ''|| Nandita Menon|| [[Hindi]]\n|-\n| 2015 || ''[[Amar Akbar Anthony (2015 film)|Amar Akbar Anthony]] ''|| Gouri (Cameo)|| Malayalam\n|-\n| 2019 || ''[[Action (2019 film)|Action]] ''||Kiara || Tamil\n|-\n|-2019 || ''[[Action (2019 film)|Action]] ''||Kiara || Tamil\n|}\n\n==Other Works==\n=== Television Serial ===\n* ''[[Vighnaharta Ganesha]] As Devi Parvati'' <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.india.com/buzz/akanksha-puri-of-calendar-girl-all-set-for-tv-debut-as-goddess-parvati-on-sony-1993345/|title=Akanksha Puri of Calendar Girl all set for TV debut as Goddess Parvati on Sony!|last=Mulla|first=Zainab|date=2017-04-04|work=India.com|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.jagran.com/entertainment/tv-akanksha-puri-is-new-parvati-in-tv-show-vighnaharta-ganesh-16583075.html|title=\u0915\u0948\u0932\u0947\u0902\u0921\u0930 \u0917\u0930\u094d\u0932 \u0938\u0947 \u092a\u093e\u0930\u094d\u0935\u0924\u0940 \u092c\u0928 \u0917\u092f\u0940 \u0939\u0948\u0902 \u0906\u0915\u093e\u0902\u0915\u094d\u0937\u093e \u092a\u0941\u0930\u0940, \u0935\u093f\u0918\u094d\u0928\u0939\u0930\u094d\u0924\u093e \u0917\u0923\u0947\u0936 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u090f\u0915 \u0928\u092f\u093e \u0905\u0935\u0924\u093e\u0930|work=jagran|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref>\n\n=== Music Video ===\n* ''[http://purefilmy.com/2017/06/12/jahaan-tum-ho-video-song/ Jahaan Tum Ho]'' with Shrey Singhal (2017)<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hxe362w66GI \"Jahaan Tum Ho Video Song and chitthi | Shrey Singhal | Latest Song 2016 | T-Series\"]</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mid-day.com/articles/bollywood-starlet-actress-madhur-bhandarkar-calendar-girl-chauffeur-cops-damage-to-mercedes-mumbai-news/18030198|title=Madhur Bhandarkar s Calendar Girl takes chauffeur to cops for damage to Mercedes|work=mid-day|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bollywoodlife.com/news-gossip/sidharth-shukla-denies-dating-akanksha-puri/|title=Sidharth Shukla DENIES dating Akanksha Puri!|last=Banerjee|first=Urmimala|access-date=2017-12-12|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Akanksha-Puri-and-her-Calendar-Girls-director-have-a-lot-in-common/articleshow/48845709.cms|title=Akanksha Puri and her 'Calendar Girls' director have a lot in common - Times of India|work=The Times of India|access-date=2017-12-12}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons}}\n*{{Bollywood Hungama|6163891}}\n*{{IMDb name}}\n*[http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/calendar-girls-a-very-emotional-film-akanksha-puri/ Indian Express]\n*[http://www.ibtimes.co.in/interview-salman-khan-reason-i-am-into-industry-says-calendar-girls-actress-akanksha-puri-647889 IBTimes]\n*[http://www.mid-day.com/articles/calendar-girls-has-a-character-inspired-by-shilpa-shettys-life/16547193 Mid-day]\n*[http://www.rediff.com/movies/interview/it-was-difficult-to-shoot-in-a-bikini/20150727.htm Rediff]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Puri, Akanksha}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Indian film actresses]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Hindi cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Tamil cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Malayalam cinema]]\n[[Category:Actresses in Kan